<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BrAPI - A API mais brasileira!</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/index/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="left">
            <img src="/index/apiLogo.png">
            <span>BrApi</span>
        </div>

        <div class="center">
            <a href="/docs" class="nav-item">
                Docs
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="arrow-icon">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                        d="M8.25 3.75H19.5a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75v11.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.5 0V6.31L5.03 20.03a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06-1.06L17.69 5.25H8.25a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.5Z"
                        clip-rule="evenodd">
                    </path>
                </svg>
            </a>

            <a href="/dashboard" class="nav-item">
                Dashboard
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="arrow-icon">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                        d="M8.25 3.75H19.5a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75v11.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.5 0V6.31L5.03 20.03a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06-1.06L17.69 5.25H8.25a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.5Z"
                        clip-rule="evenodd">
                    </path>
                </svg>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="right">
            <div class="hamburger" id="hamburger">
                <span></span>
                <span></span>
                <span></span>
            </div>
            <button onclick="window.location.href='/login'">Login</button>
        </div>
    </header>
    <div class="mobile-menu" id="mobileMenu">
        <a href="#" class="nav-item">Docs</a>
        <a href="#" class="nav-item">Dashboard</a>
    </div>
    <div class="container1">
        <main id="main" class="home-layout">
            <section>
                <div>
                    <h1 class="special">
                        A API Mais brasileira, com o toque Brasileiro
                    </h1>
                    <p>
                        A BrApi é uma API leve e descomplicada, criada pra facilitar o trabalho com dados brasileiros, permitindo validar CPF, gerar informações e integrar tudo de forma simples e direta.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-actions">
                    <a href="/docs" class="btn primary">Começar agora</a>
                    <a href="/api" class="btn secondary">Ver API</a>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section>
                <div class="api-example">

                    <div class="example-block">
                        <div class="example-header">
                            Request
                        </div>
                        <div class="code-block">
                            <%- code %>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="example-block">
                        <div class="example-header">
                            Resposta <span class="status success">200 OK</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="code-block">
                            <%- response %>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </section>
            <section>

            </section>
        </main>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <div class="footer-content">

            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>BrApi</h3>
                <p>API Brasileira open source para desenvolvedores.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-section">
                <h4>Links</h4>
                <a href="#">Docs</a>
                <a href="#">GitHub</a>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="footer-bottom">
            <p>© 2026 BrApi • Projeto Indie ;3</p>
        </div>
        </div>
    <script src="/index/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>